name: She and Her Colors
description:
She has the power of colors in her hands.
You know my collection called "Ellas". 
Each one of "Ellas" has a story to tell, a personality and a message for you.
This time I wanted to give a gift to a great artist friend. 
I thought: What would one of my characters look like if she were my artist friend?
Here is the result, "Ella" has the magic of colors in her hands.

2D digital animation on offer. 
Animation resolution 1750px x 2350px in GIF format.

Creation date: September 25, 2021 
Technique: Digital drawing and 2D animation 
Software: Medibang Pain Pro.

The artwork may not be reproduced commercially. The author reserves the right to use the image of the work for merchandising.

Thank you for supporting my work!
